{%- comment -%}
  Enquiry button.
  Renders the "Enquire on WhatsApp" button which, instead of redirecting to
  WhatsApp, opens the existing cart drawer in "enquiry mode" (the .is-enquiry
  state) showing the enquiry form. The drawer markup, styles and submit logic
  live in snippets/cart-drawer.liquid.

  Product details are passed via data attributes (the cart drawer is rendered
  globally and has no product context, so the product name/url are read from
  here on click).

  Used by templates:
    - product.b2b-enquiry-product.json
    - product.enquiry-only-product.json
{%- endcomment -%}

<button
  type="button"
  class="b2b-enquire-now-btn"
  data-enquiry-open
  data-product-name="{{ product.title | escape }}"
  data-product-url="{{ shop.secure_url }}{{ product.url }}"
  style="display:inline-block; padding:12px 24px; background-color:#000000; color:#ffffff; border:none; cursor:pointer; text-decoration:none; border-radius:6px; font-weight:600;">
  Enquire Now
</button>
